octetos-coreutils
------------------------------------------
octetos::coreutils es una libreria capaz de realizar algunas de las funcion
del paquete coreutils pero a travez de una API C++.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  liboctetos-core0-2.62.1beta-1bl1
  liboctetos-coreutils-devel-0.17.0alpha-1bl1
  liboctetos-coreutils0-0.17.0alpha-1bl1
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-3
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  liboctetos-core-devel-2.62.1beta-1bl1
  libtool-2.5.4-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/azaeldevel/octetos-coreutils

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/azaeldevel/octetos-coreutils/archive/refs/tags/0.17.0-alpha.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack octetos-coreutils-0.17.0alpha-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./octetos-coreutils-0.17.0alpha-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/octetos-coreutils-0.17.0alpha-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/octetos-coreutils-0.17.0alpha-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liboctetos-coreutils0-0.17.0alpha-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liboctetos-coreutils-devel-0.17.0alpha-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(octetos-coreutils)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/octetos-coreutils.README
  /usr/share/doc/octetos-coreutils/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/octetos-coreutils/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/octetos-coreutils/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/octetos-coreutils/INSTALL
  /usr/share/doc/octetos-coreutils/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/octetos-coreutils/README
  /usr/share/doc/octetos-coreutils/TODO

(liboctetos-coreutils0)
  /usr/bin/cygoctetos-coreutils-0.dll

(liboctetos-coreutils-devel)
  /usr/include/octetos/coreutils/shell.hh
  /usr/lib/liboctetos-coreutils.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/octetos-coreutils.pc

